Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用樹葉做魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是魚 這是章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 不是海星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}海星堂書店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘 你要這個麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 魚的圖籍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚類圖鑒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鮭魚 甘塩味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要吃麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘 你看 這個像鰈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}鰈<カレイ>：比目魚的一種,體型側扁,生活在淺海中,有些種類可遊入港灣和江河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鰈?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有種一邊長著兩隻眼睛的魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個很像河豚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許偷懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷什麼懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剪子剪就是偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是大人的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 都幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡子上邊有個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不讓把橡子拿回家裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果麗奈大哭了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡子有蟲子 樹葉也幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落葉?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的都夾在書裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾在書裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘 先去洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉 要走了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}落葉水族館



